ting story for many aspiring leaders.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/meet-shankh-mitra-indian-origin-executive-ranked-second-highest-paid-ceo-in-the-world-after-elon-musk/articleshow/131996462.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/meet-shankh-mitra-indian-origin-executive-ranked-second-highest-paid-ceo-in-the-world-after-elon-musk/articleshow/131996462.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-25T21:26:03+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131997695,imgsize-56610.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Kash Patel's girlfriend says it's an honor to sing national anthem at Freedom250, she is not taking payment]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131996902.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/kash-patels-girlfriend-says-its-an-honor-to-sing-national-anthem-at-freedom250-she-is-not-taking-payment/articleshow/131996902.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/kash-patels-girlfriend-says-its-an-honor-to-sing-national-anthem-at-freedom250-she-is-not-taking-payment/articleshow/131996902.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-25T20:39:30+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131997122,imgsize-72798.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Controversial Streamer Johnny Somali loses South Korea appeal, court upholds six-month prison sentence]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131996309.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Johnny Somali’s appeal has been rejected b